data.description: This 2016 1 1/2 story 4 bed & 3 full bath home features 2702 sq. ft. and is located in the very desirable Saratoga-Cibolo Community! The main floor offers a dedicated office & spacious living room, a private hallway leads to a full bath and two guest bedrooms w/ large walk-in closets. The living room has high ceiling and opens to the dining area & eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops and a large island. The large primary suite features a spacious bath w/ separate shower and tub, double vanity, and a monster walk-in closet. The second floor highlights a fourth bedroom with a full en suite bath (second master) and large walk in closet. This home has private back yard and has a large covered back patio. This community has a lap pool, kids pool, splash pad, playground, and a 2 mile walking trail.
